This app is designed to run under a typical java servlet container such as Tomcat, and has been tested under Tomcat 7

Database:
The app uses Hypersonic HSQLDB. To create the database, run the following:
java -cp <app install dir>/WEB-INF/lib/hsqldb.jar org.hsqldb.util.DatabaseManagerSwing
Use the following parameters:
-- Type: HSQLDB Database Engine Standalone
-- Driver: org.hsqldb.jdbcDriver
-- URL: jdbc:hsqldb:file:<file location. I use /opt/PingOne/Sample/db>
-- User: SA
-- Password: 2Federate
